Class DBUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gck.DBUtil

  • public class DBUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper for ResultSet to generate various models including, DefaultTableModel, DefaultComboBoxModel, DefaultListModel and data Vectors
